726884f-a.title: Queens: Hollis Avenue - 187th Place
726884f-a.text:
Hollis Ave., south side, at about 187th Flace., showing an old
farm house at the rear of William Moog house.
Sept. 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

726993f-c.title: Queens: Jamaica Avenue - 187th Place
726993f-c.text:
Jamaica Ave., at the N.E. corner of 187th Place, showing in a set
of three views the W. J. Allen farmhouse of 1860. T. T. Husson was
the owner in 1873. It was demolished in 1934.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
